# ==============================================================================
# Agentic coding tooling
# ==============================================================================
# Philosophy: ignore *local / personal / state* files, keep *shared* config
# (CLAUDE.md, AGENTS.md, .cursor/rules/, .github/copilot-instructions.md, etc.)
# committed so your team and the agents share the same instructions.
#
# Each vendor has a commented-out "whole directory" line. Uncomment it only if
# your team does NOT commit that tool's shared config.

# --- Anthropic / Claude Code --------------------------------------------------
CLAUDE.local.md
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/.session*
.claude/todos/
.claude/shell-snapshots/
.claude/statsig/
# .claude/                      # uncomment to ignore the entire directory

# --- OpenAI Codex CLI ---------------------------------------------------------
AGENTS.override.md
.codex/
# AGENTS.md is the cross-tool standard — keep it committed

# --- Cursor -------------------------------------------------------------------
.cursor/cache/
.cursorindexingignore
# .cursor/                      # keep .cursor/rules/ committed; uncomment to nuke

# --- GitHub Copilot -----------------------------------------------------------
# No repo-level ignore file; exclusions are configured in GitHub org settings.
# .github/copilot-instructions.md is meant to be committed.

# --- Cline / Roo Code ---------------------------------------------------------
.cline/cache/
.roo/cache/
# .clinerules and .cline/rules/ are usually committed

# --- Windsurf -----------------------------------------------------------------
.windsurf/cache/
# .windsurfrules and .windsurf/rules/ are usually committed

# --- Google Gemini CLI / Code Assist ------------------------------------------
.gemini/
# GEMINI.md is usually committed
# .aiexclude is committed (it's the ignore-list itself)

# --- Amazon Q / Kiro ----------------------------------------------------------
.amazonq/cache/
.kiro/cache/

# --- Continue.dev -------------------------------------------------------------
.continue/

# --- Zed assistant ------------------------------------------------------------
.zed/

# --- Aider --------------------------------------------------------------------
.aider*
!.aider.conf.yml
!.aiderignore
.aider.chat.history.md
.aider.input.history
.aider.llm.history
.aider.tags.cache.v*/

# --- Tabnine / Codeium / Supermaven (editor-level, occasional local state) ----
.tabnine/
.codeium/

# --- MCP (Model Context Protocol) ---------------------------------------------
# .mcp.json is often committed, BUT it can hold tokens/secrets — review before
# committing. Local override below is always ignored:
.mcp.local.json

# --- Generic agent scratch / logs ---------------------------------------------
.ai/
.agent/
*.agent.log

# ==============================================================================
# Secrets (agents should never index or commit these)
# ==============================================================================
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
!.env.template
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
secrets/

